    {
      "ResourceTypes": [
        "microsoft.dbformysql/servers"
      ],
      "Description": "Using a template to create a MySQL server with the **Replica** value is not idempotent. The server is created successfully the first time. However, deploying the template when the replica server already exists returns an error."
    },
